The Medical & Dental Clinic provides the basic health services to the students and personnel namely: 
 1. Conduct of Physical Health Examination;
2. Giving attention to daily consultations and treatments;
3. Issuance of medical certificates;
4. Giving attention to emergency cases/during athletics;\5. Making referrals of special cases to proper authorities;
6. Conduct of lectures/counseling on management of illness; and
7. Establishment of linkages among other health agencies.

The Medical and Dental Clinic provides services like:
1. Conduct of Annual Dental Examination for Elementary, High School & Senior High School Students;
2. Giving attention to dental consultations and treatments;
3. Performance of oral prophylaxis;
4. Performance of dental extraction;
5. Making referrals of special cases to proper authorities; 6. Conduct of chair side instruction/ lectures; and
6. Issuance of dental certificates.
